content: AI diving into city vibes now, and investors can't get enough. They're into the live predictions, but ngl, the pressure to keep innovating is intense. Every challenge is just a stepping stone to make our AI even smarter.

Just had a deep dive into our AI's urban model. It's now predicting how new developments will ripple through the market. It's like we're giving the AI a crystal ball, but the real test is making those predictions actionable in real-time.
